com.ephesoft.gxt.core.shared.util.logging

Class UILogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.logging.Logger
      • com.ephesoft.gxt.core.shared.util.logging.UILogger

  • public final class UILogger
extends java.util.logging.Logger
    Logger which will be responsible for doing the client side logging.

    Client Side logging is achieved using the emulation . GWT emulates the Logger

    Version:
    1.0.
    Author:
    Ephesoft
